  <h2>Feel free to suggest ideas for Commune2 enhancement, or give us feedback on existing suggestions.</h2><br />
  <h2>Have an idea, but not specific to Commune2? Then go to the <%= link_to "new idea", new_idea_path %> page.</h2>
  </td></tr></table>
